  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bomb Around ...and find out!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >is a platforming challenge where you play as a bomb whose sole purpose is to reach as high as possible. This is an explosive journey to compete in 3 different game modes: SpeedRun, Daily Seed and Regular play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explode your way to the top.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >but be careful, the more you explode, the less platforms there are to catch you when you fall!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charge your explosion for bigger jumps.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This simple to learn, hard to master mechanic, combined with the freedom to aim with your mouse will surely challenge you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Unique upgrades:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up upgrades on your journey that will aid you in reaching new heights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/3a2c3c82a72e8426a8d3338609ade4a4.poster.avif?t=1744466045\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/3a2c3c82a72e8426a8d3338609ade4a4.webm?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/3a2c3c82a72e8426a8d3338609ade4a4.mp4?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>3 Different GameModes:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Normal: for those who want to explore and have fun without extra pressure, but still a chance for recognition via the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > SpeeRun: try to reach a certain height as quickly as possible to get a place on the leaderboard. (seed based)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Daily seed: compete to reach as high as possible in a mode that changes seed once every 24hr.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tutorial World:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/0f949a8329bdf857f7506cfe7b8c3de2.poster.avif?t=1744466045\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/0f949a8329bdf857f7506cfe7b8c3de2.webm?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/0f949a8329bdf857f7506cfe7b8c3de2.mp4?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good place to learn how to learn how the game works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dress up your character as you go:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shops to customize your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/8657244ff295a176e010a56c1df2ea44.poster.avif?t=1744466045\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/8657244ff295a176e010a56c1df2ea44.webm?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/8657244ff295a176e010a56c1df2ea44.mp4?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose your favorite character skin as you get more money:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are also many different bomb types you can choose between!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.poster.avif?t=1744466045\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.webm?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.mp4?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
