img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.poster.avif?t=1744466045\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.webm?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3539690/extras/f2fa55a12fcc63db6451aa87e42274dc.mp4?t=1744466045\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
